{"type": "article", "id": 59658, "title": "汤唯代言百度地图，微信推出圣诞节“袜子套装” | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-25T05:06:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 925, "name": "圣诞节"}, {"id": 261, "name": "百度"}, {"id": 408, "name": "微信"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181225122245emtsbpAY5fG8Vi76.jpeg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"O7Nb\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4320708546913475?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">汤唯加入百度地图明星代言人，</a>此外百度地图的代言人还有杨洋。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t0817cjia6s\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"2I1r\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2155043231/4319788190442804\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>张艺兴从尚美巴黎的品牌挚友升级为品牌大使。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122338bQp9I5NnXoBMHy7D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的Case</h3><p line=\"HM42\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://santatracker.google.com/tracker.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>今年的 Google “圣诞老人追踪器”已经出发了，</b></a>和往年一样来查看圣诞老人发放礼物的“进度”。用户可以在 Google Assistant 里询问 “Where is Santa”、也可以在 Android 手机和 Android Wear 手表上安装 App 追踪看<font id=\"wordhighlight_id5\" name=\"wordhighlight_word1\">圣诞老人</font>的位置、或是在搜索里找“<font id=\"wordhighlight_id6\" name=\"wordhighlight_word1\">圣诞老人”</font>直接查看。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225125215noCrgyvahbRTltJ0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.418705\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"HM42\" class=\"\">YSL 即将上市细管哑光口红，发布<b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4319815092579689?\" rel=\"nofollow\">预热广告片</a>，</b>来呈现品牌的前卫时尚理念。同时会在北京、成都、杭州等五个城市打造“不羁前行”快闪店。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=o0814kb0ksu\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"HM42\"></p><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4320792298842061?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>京东 JOY 最近和 Hello Kitty 拍了支可爱的广告片，</b></a>双方将进行合作，预示京东圣诞季开启“萌幻圣诞上京东”专场。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k0817uhb8bx\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"Ne51\">天猫超级品牌日请来伍思凯重新演绎他的经典歌曲“特别的爱给特别的你”，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4320541484052943?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>改编成了“超级的爱给超级的你”。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e0817iqipc4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"hyPt\">瑞幸咖啡联合天天 P 图，<b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUxNDQ2OTc2MQ==&amp;mid=2247486192&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b7b20afb27b96bd1a0fc70647a146f0e&amp;chksm=f944301ece33b9088ddba734a0f100fad44d3ba1a2c07fb82e33de2f707c0d99820eff29c20d&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1225NVHHpqTIXq1NofrUBlL9&amp;key=ea9727dab47f69a823ce0fb6d2c654b10569be19f8be4bda2e4b5b0a0c7ee91f91e8ea6dde836b9d31d30e8b1e38901bd6a664fe83ebcfbdbf957b7c81b62eb667c91f597fdc3b653e56b658d8075c3a&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=2Qmo8pivAuR0lUV1kSfH0irOSgbxmbcrsjKD76MADYvqxtFG94bdK0Ke5jDy1LIN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">打造了 6 款不同风格的圣诞鹿角</a>，</b>使用“天天 P 图小程序”拍摄出带有鹿角的圣诞照，还自带“变脸”效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812251226163PHWlg8dCiUEpMZ6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.399814\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"1cIK\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1835097604/4320806043267650\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>可口可乐中国在圣诞节给圣诞老人拟定了一份“劳动合同书”，</b></a>推出一系列“任务”插画，把圣诞老人的形象和公益活动的场景融合在一起，意在表达“老头一直在身边”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122632Er0dlzYWqamF4SP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122632DxwTvi73sKMbL1ES.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122633dQYi27LPg4hR1AsS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122634RvjyZDlSAOaqXox0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122634bR7JKoramY92wnNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122635XZbNyVYMt3pBxien.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"T6kn\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2MzczNjc5NQ==&amp;mid=2247484668&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e4f84c7dd9592490790fbda3c0ce0b75&amp;chksm=eab61848ddc1915eb1df1fc77230afcdfc2efea66a65365b54c2c6b64ca96f2fe44258d74a13&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1225MJo7FiwsEpXlRInZge6G&amp;key=ea9727dab47f69a8c84ef1b468fc0472d6d1d630058b13d810fa077381c23196ce587496c187e3f4711424edf43a6febc3c93aad2c32731d21d4ab278a410bb5d88015915d1660d12bb44a90bd497220&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=2Qmo8pivAuR0lUV1kSfH0irOSgbxmbcrsjKD76MADYvqxtFG94bdK0Ke5jDy1LIN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微信圣诞节也出了周边，是一套“微信袜子套装”。</b></a>分别是包含微信经典设计元素的“微信气泡狗长袜套装”和表情包元素的“微信黄脸短袜套装”。不过，现在只有鹅厂内部员工能够购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122721keixgzUqdRbQuZVB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181225122730IPoXkVqHvfO0eAMc.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"T6kn\" class=\"\">根据<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/stores-finishing-the-holidays-on-a-high-note-11545566400\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>万事达</b></a>的数据显示，美国今年圣诞季11 月 1 日—12 月 19 日 零售门店的销售额增长了 5.2%，线上销售额则增长 了 18.3%。</p><p line=\"T6kn\" class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.ebrun.com/20181224/313581.shtml?eb=com_chan_lcol_fylb\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>亚马逊全球开店宣布在华推出“时尚+”项目，</b></a>通过时尚品类卖家专属服务团队，来为不同类型、不同发展阶段的卖家提供定制化服务，协助国内时尚类卖家向海外市场拓展。<br></p><p line=\"T6kn\" class=\"\">题图来自：WeStore</p>"}